fields.name: Kashke bademjan
fields.description: A tasty and simple persian appetiser. An eggplant dip with caramelized onions, roasted nuts, herbs and spices.

fields.name: Mirza ghasemi
fields.description: A great Persian dish of soft roasted aubergine in tomato and garlic sauce, with eggs cooked into it at the last minute. Ideal for making as part of a mezze meal.

fields.name: Do piyaze alo
fields.description: Do piyaze alo is a nice, simple vegetarian meal made of diced potato, tomato and onions.

fields.name: Salad olivieh
fields.description: Salad olivieh is the Persian version of chicken salad and potato salad, rolled into one amazing dish that is loved by most who try it.

fields.name: Noon panir sabzi
fields.description: Noon panir sabzi is a Persian platter served with a delicious mix of fresh herbs, mint, walnuts, radishes feta cheese and flat bread.

fields.name: Baghali polo
fields.description: Baghali polo is a popular Iranian dish of rice, fava beans and dill. It is made by cooking rice and green broad beans in boiling water. This dish can be served in all varieties.

fields.name: Zereshk polo ba morgh
fields.description: Zereshk Polo ba Morgh is a Persian classic made with Zereshk (barberries), Morgh (chicken), and Polo, which is the steamed and fluffy Persian rice.

fields.name: Khoreshte gheymeh bademjoon
fields.description: Lamb Aubergine Stew with Yellow Split Peas gives you an idea of the main ingredients of this dish.

fields.name: Khoreshte ghorme sabzi
fields.description: A stew made of herbs like parsley and coriander; cooked with kidney beans and lamb. Vegetarian ghormeh sabzi has mushrooms rather than meat.

fields.name: Khoreste fesenjoon ba morgh
fields.description: This stew is flavored with pomegranate paste, ground walnuts and spices like turmeric, cinnamon, cardamom, and rosebud.

fields.name: Baklava
fields.description: Baklava is a rich, sweet dessert pastry made of layers of filo filled with chopped nuts and sweetened and held together with honey.

fields.name: Faloodeh shirazi
fields.description: Faloodeh is a traditional Iranian cold dessert similar to a sorbet. It consists of thin vermicelli-sized noodles made from starch in a semi-frozen syrup.

fields.name: Bastani sonnati
fields.description: Bastani is an Iranian ice cream made from milk, eggs, sugar, rose water, saffron, vanilla, and pistachios. It is known widely as Persian ice cream.

fields.name: Noon khamei
fields.description: Noon khamei is a filled choux pastry ball with a typically sweet and moist filling of whipped cream, custard, pastry cream, or ice cream.

fields.name: Ranginak
fields.description: Ranginak is a Shirazi sweet made from Dates, nuts, cinnamon. It's makes a good combination with tea.

fields.name: Doogh
fields.description: Doogh is a cold savory yogurt-based beverage that is mixed with salt.

fields.name: Araghe bidmeshk
fields.description: Strengthens the nervous system Facilitates the digestion Helps with stress-related headaches, tachycardia, anxiety and mood.

fields.name: Araghe gol gav zaban
fields.description: Gol gav zaban flower has a sweet honey-like taste and is one of the few truly blue-colored edible substances.

fields.name: Mojito
fields.description: Mojito flavors are sweetness, citrus, and herbaceous mint, which makes it a popular summer drink.

fields.name: White russian
fields.description: White russian is a cocktail made with vodka, coffee liqueur and cream served with ice in an Old Fashioned glass.

fields.name: Bloody mary
fields.description: Bloody mary is a cocktail containing vodka, tomato juice, and other spices and flavorings including celery and lemon juice.

fields.name: Espresso
fields.description: A small amount of nearly boiling water is forced under pressure (expressed) through finely-ground coffee beans.

fields.name: Masala chai
fields.description: Masala chai is a flavoured tea beverage made by brewing black tea with a mixture of aromatic Indian spices and herbs.

fields.name: Orange juice
fields.description: Orange juice is a liquid extract of the orange tree fruit, produced by squeezing or reaming oranges.

fields.name: Watermelon juice
fields.description: A soft sweet natural juice. No added suger.

fields.name: Berry juice
fields.description: A soft sweet natural juice. No added suger.
